### Health
# 用于 smoke test，验证服务是否成功启动
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/health
Accept: application/json

### Register
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice",
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "Passw0rd!23",
  "code": "123456"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "account": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "Passw0rd!23"
}

### Save token (manually replace after login/register)
@token = REPLACE_WITH_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Get current user
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Save my profile draft
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/profiles/me/draft
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bio": "后端开发，专注分布式系统与工程实践。",
  "experiences": [
    {
      "title": "技术负责人",
      "organization": "MemberWiki",
      "description": "负责后端架构与接口设计",
      "start_date": "2025-09-01",
      "end_date": "2026-06-30"
    }
  ],
  "awards": [
    {
      "name": "校级创新竞赛一等奖",
      "level": "校级",
      "year": 2025,
      "description": "项目总负责"
    }
  ],
  "proof_file_ids": []
}

### Submit review
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/profiles/me/submit-review
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Search members
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/search/members?keyword=技术&page=1&page_size=20&sort_by=updated_at&sort_order=desc

### Admin review list
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/reviews?page=1&page_size=20&status=pending
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Approve review
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/reviews/1/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "comment": "资料完整，审核通过"
}

### Reject review
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/reviews/2/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "奖项证明材料不完整，请补充后重新提交"
}
